1
00:00:06,248 --> 00:00:08,778
Visa granting officer—
Nityānanda Prabhu.

2
00:00:08,968 --> 00:00:12,294
[Visa Granting Officer of the Spiritual World]

3
00:00:12,780 --> 00:00:16,940
heno nitāi bine bhāi, 
rādhā-kṛṣṇa pāite nāi

4
00:00:16,940 --> 00:00:20,410
nitāiyer koruṇā habe, 
braje rādhā-kṛṣṇa pābe

5
00:00:20,410 --> 00:00:23,180
[Manaḥ-Śikṣā
by Śrīla Narottam Dās Ṭhākur]

6
00:00:23,180 --> 00:00:27,880
Visa granting officer, Governer; 
visa granting office,

7
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:31,170
Dhameshvar Nabadwīp,
Nityānanda Prabhu.

8
00:00:31,170 --> 00:00:35,550
yatha yatha gaura-padaravinde 
vindeta bhaktim krta punya-rasih

9
00:00:35,551 --> 00:00:41,971
tatha tathot-sarpati hrdya-kasmad 
radha-padambhoja-sudhambu rasih
[Ccd: 88]

10
00:00:41,986 --> 00:00:45,801
“Yes!”, Prabodhānanda says, 
“Give all your attention

11
00:00:45,801 --> 00:00:50,861
those who are sukritivan,
sumedhasaḥ,

12
00:00:50,861 --> 00:00:56,693
they will take the suggestion,

13
00:00:56,693 --> 00:01:01,148
feel the compulsion
to offer themselves exclusivly

14
00:01:01,148 --> 00:01:03,728
to the lotus feet 
of Guru and Gaurāṅga.”

15
00:01:05,217 --> 00:01:06,507
Where?

16
00:01:08,217 --> 00:01:12,308
Nitāi, nitāi-pada-kamala, 
koṭi-candra-suśītala

17
00:01:12,308 --> 00:01:18,508
We have to—as Dās Goswāmī did, 
as Kṛṣṇadās Goswāmī did—

18
00:01:18,518 --> 00:01:21,626
get the shelter of the lotus feet 
of Nityānanda Prabhu.

19
00:01:21,626 --> 00:01:25,795
Guru Maharāj, “Doyal Nitāi, 
Doyal Nitāi, Doyal Nitāi …”

20
00:01:25,795 --> 00:01:30,150
Take shelter of the lotus feet 
of Nityānanda,

21
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:33,523
and Nityānanda will give 
the connection with Gaurāṅga.

22
00:01:33,523 --> 00:01:38,819
bhaja gaurāńga kaha gaurāńga 
laha gaurāńgera nām

23
00:01:38,819 --> 00:01:39,999
[song by Kṛṣṇadās Kavirāj Gosvāmī]

24
00:01:39,999 --> 00:01:41,328
Mahāprabhu told them,
 

25
00:01:41,328 --> 00:01:44,058
yāre dekha, tāre kaha 
‘kṛṣṇa’-upadeśa—
[Cc: 2.7.128]

26
00:01:44,058 --> 00:01:48,532
“Tell everyone about Kṛṣṇa.”
And Nityānanda’s saying,

27
00:01:48,532 --> 00:01:52,303
“Not enough time!
Bhaja Gaurāṅga,

28
00:01:52,303 --> 00:01:58,283
worship Gaurāṅga,
chant the name of Gaurāṅga!

29
00:01:58,283 --> 00:02:01,823
gaura-gatha grnanti

30
00:02:01,823 --> 00:02:06,218
as do the members 
of Śrī Chaitanya Sāraswat Maṭh.

31
00:02:06,218 --> 00:02:11,178
Their preoccupation, occupation, 
preoccupation

32
00:02:11,178 --> 00:02:14,807
is singing the glories
of Mahāprabhu.

33
00:02:14,807 --> 00:02:18,248
That means Rādhārāṇī.

34
00:02:18,518 --> 00:02:22,628
yadi gaura na haita, tabe ki haita,
kemane dharitām de

35
00:02:22,628 --> 00:02:28,630
rādhāra mahimā, prema-rasa-sīmā
jagate jānāta ke?

36
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:35,319
Vāsu Ghoṣ said, “This is why
Kṛṣṇa descended as Mahāprabhu—

37
00:02:35,333 --> 00:02:40,483
to proclaim the glories of Rādhārāṇī 
to everyone.

38
00:02:41,355 --> 00:02:45,747
And the glories of Her supreme love,
Her kṛṣṇa-prema.”

39
00:02:45,747 --> 00:02:50,387
This is the foundation 
of the Kṛṣṇa consciousness movement.

